        "setup": "In Avo, open [Workspace Settings → Service Accounts](https://www.avo.app/schemas/default?settings=service-accounts) (or follow the steps in [Authentication](https://www.avo.app/docs/reference/public-api/authentication.md#creating-service-accounts)). Create a service account, copy the generated final service-account name and secret once, then send them to the API as HTTP Basic auth using base64-encoded `name:secret` in the `authorization` header. Only workspace admins can create service accounts."
